    <item>
      <title>动量贸易创纪录的一年即将结束，裂缝不断扩大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/record-year-for-momentum-trade-is-ending-with-widening-cracks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管特朗普贸易大获全胜，人工智能也引发了狂热，但今年在各个市场赚钱都十分艰难。现在，就连推动美国股市上涨的贸易也开始出现动摇迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/record-year-for-momentum-trade-is-ending-with-widening-cracks</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Dec 2024 22:05:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>耶伦称财政部将在 1 月中旬达到新的债务上限</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/yellen-says-treasury-to-hit-new-debt-limit-in-mid-january</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政部长珍妮特耶伦表示，财政部很可能在 1 月中旬某个时候开始采取特殊会计措施，以避免突破美国债务上限，并敦促立法者采取行动捍卫美国的“充分信任和信用”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/yellen-says-treasury-to-hit-new-debt-limit-in-mid-january</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Dec 2024 21:51:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
